com.culturemesh.android

Class NetworkSummaryAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • <any>
      • com.culturemesh.android.NetworkSummaryAdapter

  • public class NetworkSummaryAdapter
extends <any>
    This functions as the recyclerview adapter for the listview in ViewProfileActivity, where the user can view other users' subscribed networks.
